\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 09, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pnt1665702893811.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pnt1665702893811.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pnt1665702893811.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pnt1665702893811\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__configmanager_putprop_420640\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets a property to a specified value that has not been set.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__topic_d128273e1_d128274e1_d128275e1\">\n<dl class=\"dl\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__dl_bhn_hgv_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\">General method</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104pnt1665702893811_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__codeblock_i2d_jgv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">voidputProp(StringPropertyName, StringPropertyValue)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\">Specialized method</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104pnt1665702893811_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__codeblock_a3g_lgv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">voidputProp(StringComponentName, StringPropertyName, StringPropertyValue)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__topic_d90802e1_d90803e1_d90804e1_d90805e1_d90806e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729252e81\">Parameters</h2><var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyName</var><dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__parml_xwr_ngv_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Property name consisting of a series of period-separated identifiers. For\n                  example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.component.average.name</code></dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PropertyValue</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Value to give to the property.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Component name for the property to be set. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var> is\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">null</code> or asterisk (*), the property is set for all\n                  components.</dd>\n</dl></section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__topic_d90807e1_d90808e1_d90809e1_d90810e1_d90811e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729252e126\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__p_d128291e1_d128292e1_d128293e1\">The following properties can be set with\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">configManager.putProp</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Configuration Manager Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\">Property </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Component name </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">apsname</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Name of the application shell </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">asnFile</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Name of the assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">commandline</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Command line instructions </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ininame</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Name of the initialization file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">workdir</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Working directory for the Configuration Manager </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">handler</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pnt1665702893811__table_d15308e1_d15309e1_d15310e1__entry__2\">Name of call handler; one of\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">uvm</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">jvm</code> or\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">rmi</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__topic_d90812e1_d90813e1_d90814e1_d90815e1_d90816e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729252e255\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__d5995e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__topic_d90817e1_d90818e1_d90819e1_d90820e1_d90821e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729252e265\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__p_d128303e1_d128304e1_d128305e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">putProp</code> is a static method for\n            class <code class=\"ph codeph\">configManager</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following line of Java code shows the use of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">putProp</code> method with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">commandline</code> property. It assigns that subset to all subsets:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104pnt1665702893811_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"pnt1665702893811__codeblock_pvc_lhv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ConfigManager.putProp (null, \"commandline\", \"/ini=c:/uniface/adm/usys.ini\" + \"/asn=c:/uniface/adm/usys.asn\");</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530988\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530988\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ConfigManager.putProp Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 09, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sets a property to a specified value that has not been set. General method Explain this code voidputProp(StringPropertyName, StringPropertyValue) Copy Specialized method Explain this code voidputProp(StringComponentName, StringPropertyName, StringPropertyValue) Copy Parameters PropertyName Property name consisting of a series of period-separated identifiers. For example, uniface.component.average.name PropertyValue Value to give to the property. ComponentName Component name for the property to be set. If ComponentName is null or asterisk (*), the property is set for all components. Properties The following properties can be set with configManager.putProp : Table 1. Configuration Manager Properties Property Description name Component name apsname Name of the application shell asnFile Name of the assignment file commandline Command line instructions ininame Name of the initialization file workdir Working directory for the Configuration Manager handler Name of call handler; one of uvm (default) or jvm or rmi Return Values None Description putProp is a static method for class configManager . The following line of Java code shows the use of the putProp method with the commandline property. It assigns that subset to all subsets: Explain this code ConfigManager.putProp (null, \"commandline\", \"/ini=c:/uniface/adm/usys.ini\" + \"/asn=c:/uniface/adm/usys.asn\"); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}